            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hope I could give zero stars for the college . Believe me it is totally worst if you want to make something great of your future then I recommend don't take admission in this college. Well the school is too good but when it comes to college, it's tooo bad at the college, no proper management staff, no proper teaching staff (last year 4 teachers got changed for just one subject, which caused a massive loss of portion), even the supervisor doesn't help the students when they need him and his help (but at the start we are promised that all our problems would be resolved if we complain about the same in time, but when we did the same the response was try to adjust) when we are suffering from headache or itching in eyes we are not allowed to rest instead the answer what we get is change your steam. Overall I'm too depressed with this college 😑🤯",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
