          "reviewBody": "This is one of the top most trusted and named english convent school in pune. This school had church in its own campus and here mostly teachers are sisters and fathers.\nThey have great teaching faculty and also the method of teaching is wonderful. This school had not so big campus but is is enough for the students that they intake.\nThe quality of education is respected.\nSo over all if you are looking for convent school then this school is a best match.",
